    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1898-10-13T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1898-10-13T12:00:00-05:00" n="801"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d801">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Hay</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Day</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date ana="#date_imprecise-inferred-from-document-content"
                            calendar="gregorian" notAfter="1898-10-13T23:59:59-05:00"
                            notBefore="1898-10-13T12:00:00-05:00" when="1898-10-13">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 13, 1898</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The President sees no reason for departing from instructions already given, but
                    many reasons for adhering strictly to terms of protocol concerning Cuba. We must
                    carry out the spirit and letter of the resolution of Congress. The Commission
                    will use its own best judgment as to pressing to definite conclusions.</p>
                <closer>
                    <dateline rendition="#left">
                        <date ana="#date_imprecise-inferred-from-document-content"
                            calendar="gregorian" notAfter="1898-10-13T23:59:59-05:00"
                            notBefore="1898-10-13T12:00:00-05:00" when="1898-10-13">Thursday
                            afternoon</date>.</dateline>
                    <lb/>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hay.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
